RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2010-1042. State ex rel. Neofotistos v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 09AP-712, 2010-Ohio-2065. Reported at 127 Ohio St.3d 1537, 2011-Ohio-447, 940 N.E.2d 989. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.
